Name: Draco Space X
About the game: Arcade 2D shooting game in space, in which you face enemies, full of lights and colors for your sight, you can equip new ships and conquer the trials! You will be able to face enemies in order to pass the trials, you will get new ships on the way, each one with different shooting modes, and with its own characteristics. Try to dodge the bullets and the enemies in front of you to beat each level! Lights and colors in each stage, different in each phase. More than 20 different replayable levels. Different music for each type of challenge Different ships to play, each one with different characteristics. The experience of defeating many enemies!
